{"tid":1476180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開盤 估下818之前會用咩招數黎減低示威人數","createTime":"2019-08-15T17:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T14:32:59.000Z","uid":278443,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8e45fe99c77ac5d0f7c61d473a599965a34263","tid":1476180,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"根據以往多次吹大雞遊行經驗，係遊行既一兩日前警犬會用唔同方法黎減低遊行人數，務求令到百萬遊行不再出現。<br />\n<br />\n下列係以往警犬出過既招數：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><strong>1. 唔批不反對通知書（減少公務員等絕不犯法人士）<br />\n1. 搜到燃燒彈 懷疑用黎襲擊警方<br />\n2. 搜到大量爆炸品 懷疑有人製做土製炸彈<br />\n3. 收到風黑社會進場 無差別打人<br />\n（以上3項都係增加遊行風險 嚇退想上街既人）</strong></strong></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家估下今次會出邊招</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會聽日訓醒就捉到幾個恐怖分子或者破左個軍火庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你諗到佢地會有咩新招，快D留言講下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaaa414df54af069eaaaaed481faea5f6fad845","tid":1476180,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:25:24.000Z","msg":"818見"},{"pid":"7f96f7610c7816dbf4492f32cb6b488e29a67adf","tid":1476180,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:28:35.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅機會啊！！十八區we connect，８２３和理非<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人鏈</spa